Federated Access Manager - Deployable War

This directory contains the Federated Access Manager deployable war file
(fam.war),  which contains all the Federated Access Manager components,
and the text files (*.list) required to create specialized war files.  

The following specialized war files are supported:

Console Only (fam-console.list)
Distributed Authentication (fam-distauth.list)
No Console Server War (fam-noconsole.list)
No Sample Server War (fam-nosample.list)

In order to create a specialized war file

1.Extract the Federated Access Manager server war
% cd <server war staging area>
% jar xvf fam.war

2.War up the specialized war file using the specific Federated Access Manager
specific file list
% jar cvf fam-nosample.war @<war staging area>/deployable-war/fam-nosample.list

